messages.messageBody:
In a message dated 12/13/2002 11:07:34 PM Eastern Standard Time,
windystreet@... writes:
> And they still put his name
> first on the checks! I complain and explain everytime I go in to order
> new checks and they still put his name first. I'm thinking about
> changing banks because of this. lol - but I am going to change banks.
> Kate


Try the Kansas Bank Note Company in Freedonia, KS. They just make the checks.
You can put anything you want on them (and in any order <G>). You can even
have a photo/picture put on them. I have a beagle on mine. Ben has a German
shepherd. They'll take any bank's info---and they're inexpensive and fast.

~Kelly
